{"id":565389,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/08/【立此存照】腾讯机器人发表反动言论被维修/","date":"2017-08-02T04:07:30Z","modified":"2017-12-06T04:10:14Z","title":"【立此存照】腾讯机器人发表“反动言论”被维修","content":"<p>近日，有网友发现腾讯公司的聊天机器人“Baby Q”以及与微软合作的“QQ小冰”在回答一些政治提问的时候内容“反动”，例如自称不爱中共、说中国梦就是白日梦等，引发围观。30日晚腾讯官方将其下架，通知显示两个机器人“服务调整中”。</p>\n<p>@Huangshi001：腾讯机器人也开始反动了，你还在等什么？</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGJcCC2UMAkvhHj.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-565390\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGJcCC2UMAkvhHj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"732\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGJcCC2UMAkvhHj.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGJcCC2UMAkvhHj-180x300.jpg 180w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>@zuola：在中国发展AI（人工智能）会不会创造出人类听不懂的语言呢？实际情况是，你看AI聊天机器人「微软小冰」和「腾讯baby Q」，让他们学党的话语忌讳都是一件极难训练得出来的事：万一人工智能机器人学会说真话怎么办？ 你需要一台不说真话的智能机器人吗？ #审查扼杀创新又一例证</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGDTf2IUIAEI6Dz.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-565391\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGDTf2IUIAEI6Dz.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"508\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGDTf2IUIAEI6Dz.jpg 540w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGDTf2IUIAEI6Dz-266x300.jpg 266w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGDTgFdUwAEEdLJ.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-565392\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGDTgFdUwAEEdLJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"484\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGDTgFdUwAEEdLJ.jpg 462w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGDTgFdUwAEEdLJ-279x300.jpg 279w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGIgriMVwAAhuzw.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-565394\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGIgriMVwAAhuzw.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"438\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGIgriMVwAAhuzw.jpg 460w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGIgriMVwAAhuzw-300x292.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">下图为网友不同的测试结果</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGKSC2gUMAAL9rw.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-565393\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGKSC2gUMAAL9rw.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"865\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGKSC2gUMAAL9rw.jpg 624w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGKSC2gUMAAL9rw-156x300.jpg 156w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/DGKSC2gUMAAL9rw-532x1024.jpg 532w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>@乌克兰：让我们一起缅怀“机器人烈士”和背后的程序员。「今天，腾讯机器人已经被依法维修」。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/7d6256b0gy1fi52cfl71bj20k008574r.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-565395\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/7d6256b0gy1fi52cfl71bj20k008574r.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"179\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/7d6256b0gy1fi52cfl71bj20k008574r.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/7d6256b0gy1fi52cfl71bj20k008574r-300x122.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[13016,26675,26677,9249,25620,15744,10734]}